# 🛡️ Sentinel AI — Industrial Safety Intelligence Platform

> **Multi-Agent Compound Risk Detection & Autonomous Emergency Response System**  
> *Preventing industrial disasters by breaking operational silos between IoT telemetry, permit logs, and workforce presence.*

---

## 📌 Executive Summary

Traditional SCADA systems and industrial safety monitors operate in isolated silos. They trigger alarms based on single-variable threshold breaches (e.g., gas exceeding 100 ppm) but remain **inherently blind to compound risk conditions**—scenarios where multiple sub-threshold operational parameters overlap to create catastrophic hazards.

**Sentinel AI** bridges this critical gap. By correlating real-time streams from IoT environmental sensors, active permit-to-work (PTW) records, workforce shift data, and statutory safety codes (OISD / Factory Act) into a single predictive layer, Sentinel AI identifies multi-domain hazard patterns **hours before traditional threshold systems trigger**.

---

## 🔥 Key Platform Capabilities

- **⚡ Multi-Agent Compound Risk Engine:** Asynchronously correlates gas concentration, active hot work permits, and personnel PPE compliance to calculate unified compound risk indices.
- **🗺️ Digital Twin Zone Safety Visualizer:** Interactive spatial layout mapping facility zones with real-time status telemetry and cross-domain hazard linkage banners.
- **📜 Digital Permit Intelligence (SIMOPS Protection):** Automatically cross-checks permit authorizations against live environmental telemetry, flagging dangerous simultaneous operations and issuing automated permit revocation orders.
- **🚨 Autonomous Emergency Response Orchestrator:** Triggers immediate zone evacuation advisories, logs evidence timelines, and outlines corrective action workflows during critical risk conditions.
- **🤖 Gemini Regulatory AI Copilot:** Powered by Google Gemini, providing site safety engineers with instant, grounded answers regarding OISD/Factory Act compliance and root-cause mitigation strategies.

